.hero-unit

  %h1 Hello World
  %p This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website. It includes a large callout called the hero unit and three supporting pieces of content. Use it as a starting point to create something more unique.

%h2.category Top Galleries
.row-fluid
  - Category.top.galleries.each do |g| 
    = link_to(image_tag(s3_image_path(g.cover_url)), gallery_path(g))

%h2.category Stuff Picks
.row-fluid
  - Category.stuff_picks.galleries.each do |g| 
    = link_to(image_tag(s3_image_path(g.cover_url)), gallery_path(g))

%h2.category Guess You Like
.row-fluid
  - Category.recommend.galleries.each do |g| 
    = link_to(image_tag(s3_image_path(g.cover_url)), gallery_path(g))

%h2.category Images We Have - All For YOU ( 121, 000+ )
.row-fluid
  - Gallery.all.each do |g| 
    = link_to(image_tag(s3_image_path(g.cover_url)), gallery_path(g))
